 <name>HTML_QuickForm_Rule_Spelling</name>
 <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
 <summary>A HTML_QuickForm rule plugin that checks the spelling of its values</summary>
 <description>Although browsers now have builtin spellcheckers, HTML_QuickForm_Rule_Spelling allows you to control the quality of text data submitted.

The frontend is a clientside javascript dialog that goes through the misspelt words, giving the user the option to ignore the word, add it to the dictionary or change the word given a list of suggestions.</description>
